/articolo/hall-of-fame-42/|url-status=dead|archivedate=11 April 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"acmilan.com\"/>\n\n== Notes ==\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n{{reflist|group=nb}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*{{FIFA|48549}}\n*{{NFT|1009}}\n*{{WorldFootball.net|dida}}\n*{{BDFutbol|96132}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20161019155551/http://www.bomsensofc.org.br/ ''Bom Senso FC'' official website] {{in lang|pt|en}} (Archived)\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title=Brazil squads\n| bg          = #FFDF00\n| fg          = #008000\n| bordercolor = blue\n|list1=\n{{Brazil squad 1995 Copa Am\u00e9rica}}\n{{Brazil squad 1996 CONCACAF Gold Cup}}\n{{Brazil men's football squad 1996 Summer Olympics}}\n{{Brazil squad 1997 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 1998 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 1999 Copa Am\u00e9rica}}\n{{Brazil squad 1999 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 2001 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 2001 Copa Am\u00e9rica}}\n{{Brazil squad 2002 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 2003 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 2005 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 2006 FIFA World Cup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Awards\n|bg = gold\n|fg = navy\n|list1 =\n{{Serie A Goalkeeper of the Year}}\n{{1993 Bola de Prata}}\n{{1996 Bola de Prata}}\n{{1998 Bola de Prata}}\n{{1999 Bola de Prata}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dida}}\n[[Category:1973 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Bahia]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:Esporte Clube Vit\u00f3ria players]]\n[[Category:Cruzeiro Esporte Clube players]]\n[[Category:FC Lugano players]]\n[[Category:Sport Club Corinthians Paulista players]]\n[[Category:A.C. Milan players]]\n[[Category:Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Portuguesa de Desportos players]]\n[[Category:Gr\u00eamio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense players]]\n[[Category:Sport Club Internacional players]]\n[[Category:Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Champions League winning players]]\n[[Category:Brazil youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazil under-20 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Olympic footballers of Brazil]]\n[[Category:Brazil international footballers]]\n[[Category:1995 Copa Am\u00e9rica players]]\n[[Category:1996 CONCACAF Gold Cup players]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:1997 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:1998 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:1999 Copa Am\u00e9rica players]]\n[[Category:1999 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2001 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2001 Copa Am\u00e9rica players]]\n[[Category:2002 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:2003 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2005 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2006 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:Copa Am\u00e9rica-winning players]]\n[[Category:FIFA Confederations Cup-winning players]]\n[[Category:FIFA World Cup-winning players]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Brazil]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in football]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Switzerland]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Italy]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Switzerland]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2020}}\n{{Portuguese name|de Jesus|Silva}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name                = Dida\n| image               = dida-wikipedia.png\n| caption             = Dida in 2012\n| fullname            = N\u00e9lson de Jesus Silva\n| birth_date          = {{birth date and age|1973|10|7|df=y}}\n| birth_place         = [[Irar\u00e1]], [[Bahia]], Brazil\n| height              = {{convert|1.96|m|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web | url = http