 \n| nationalyears2 = 1995 \n| nationalyears3 = 1998 \n| nationalyears4 = 1999 \n| nationalyears5 = 2000\n| nationalteam1 = Italy U-18 \n| nationalteam2 = Italy U-18 \n| nationalteam3 = [[Italy national under-21 football team|Italy U-21]] \n| nationalteam4 = Italy U-21 \n| nationalteam5 = Italy U-21\n| nationalcaps1 = 5  \n| nationalcaps2 = 2  \n| nationalcaps3 = 1  \n| nationalcaps4 = 4  \n| nationalcaps5 = 1  \n| nationalgoals1 = 1   \n| nationalgoals2 = 0   \n| nationalgoals3 = 0   \n| nationalgoals4 = 1   \n| nationalgoals5 = 0 \n| manageryears1 = 2012\n| managerclubs1 = [[A.S.D. Citt\u00e0 di Marino|Marino]]\n| pcupdate = 2012/13 season\n| ntupdate = 25, September, 2012\n}}\n'''Gennaro Scarlato''' (born 3 May 1977 in [[Naples]]) is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[association football]] and former manager (head coach) of [[A.S.D. Citt\u00e0 di Marino|Marino]] and former player as [[Defender (association football)|defender]].\n\n==Career==\n\n===Player===\n\n==== International ====\n\nHe was in the provisional squad of [[Italy national under-21 football team|Italian U-21 team]] in [[2000 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2000 UEFA U-21 Championship]] and [[Football at the 2000 Summer Olympics|2000 Olympics]], but never made any appearance.\n\n===Coach===\n\nOn 19 September 2012 he becomes the new coach of [[A.S.D. Citt\u00e0 di Marino|Marino]] (head coach) in the [[Serie D]], in place of the resigned Nunzio Iardino,<ref>http://www.marino24ore.it/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2158:citta-di-marino-mister-iardino-si-e-dimesso&catid=49:calcio&Itemid=155</ref><ref>http://www.marino24ore.it/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2176:citta-di-marino-il-presidente-ritira-le-dimissioni-scarlato-nuovo-mister&catid=49:calcio&Itemid=155</ref> until 30 October 2012 when he was sacked.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.figc.it/nazionali/DettaglioConvocato?codiceConvocato=1510 FIGC] {{in lang|it}}\n*[http://www.acspezia.com/teamDetail.php?id=15 acspezia.com] {{in lang|it}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-sports}}\n{{succession box|before=[[Dario Marcolin]]|title=[[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]] captain|years=2004\u20132005|after=[[Francesco Montervino]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Scarlato, Gennaro}}\n[[Category:1977 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Italian footballers]]\n[[Category:Italy under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Italy youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:S.S.C. Napoli players]]\n[[Category:L.R. Vicenza Virtus players]]\n[[Category:Torino F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Udinese Calcio players]]\n[[Category:Ternana Calcio players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Crotone players]]\n[[Category:Spezia Calcio players]]\n[[Category:Ravenna F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Frosinone Calcio players]]\n[[Category:Cosenza Calcio players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:Serie B players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Naples]]\n[[Category:S.S. Ischia Isolaverde players]]\n[[Category:A.S.D. Citt\u00e0 di Marino Calcio]]\n", "name_user": "Robby.is.on", "label": "safe", "comment": "Standardise section headings. Minor corrections.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gennaro_Scarlato"}
